KET_READING_UNITS = [{'name': '词汇基础', 'description': '掌握KET核心词汇，学会词汇记忆方法', 'sort_order': 1, 'lessons': [{'title': '日常生活词汇', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 1, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': 'KET考试需要掌握约1500个核心词汇。这节课我们从最常用的日常生活词汇开始！'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '日常生活高频词', 'content': '家庭成员：parents, brother, sister, cousin, uncle, aunt\n食物：breakfast, lunch, dinner, snack, fruit, vegetable\n衣物：shirt, dress, jacket, shoes, trousers, coat\n身体：head, shoulder, knee, arm, leg, hand\n颜色：red, blue, green, yellow, black, white, brown'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '用英语描述你的家庭早餐', 'solution': "例句：My family has breakfast at 7 o'clock. My father eats bread with butter. My mother has fruit and yogurt. I drink milk and eat cereal."}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'Fill in: I need to buy a new ___ for the winter. (coat / trousers / shirt)', 'solution': 'Answer: coat. 冬天需要外套(coat)，trousers是裤子，shirt是衬衫。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': "选择正确答案：My ___ is my mother's brother. (uncle / cousin / aunt)", 'options': ['uncle', 'cousin', 'aunt', 'brother'], 'answer': 'uncle'}, {'question': '选择正确答案：Apples and bananas are ___. (fruits / vegetables / drinks)', 'options': ['fruits', 'vegetables', 'drinks', 'snacks'], 'answer': 'fruits'}, {'question': '选择正确答案：You wear these on your feet. (shoes / jacket / hat)', 'options': ['shoes', 'jacket', 'hat', 'gloves'], 'answer': 'shoes'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '词汇记忆技巧：分类记忆法——将词汇按主题分组，建立联想。'}]}}, {'title': '学校与学习词汇', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 2, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': 'KET考试中关于学校和学习的词汇出现频率很高。这节课我们来系统学习这些词汇。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '学校相关词汇', 'content': '科目：math, English, science, history, geography, art, music\n教室物品：book, pen, pencil, ruler, eraser, desk, chair\n学校场所：classroom, library, playground, office, canteen\n学习动作：read, write, learn, study, answer, ask, explain, understand'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '用英语描述你的课程表', 'solution': '例句：On Monday, I have math in the morning and English in the afternoon. My favorite subject is science because we do experiments.'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'Fill in: Can I ___ your pen? I forgot mine at home. (borrow / lend / take)', 'solution': 'Answer: borrow. borrow=借入（从别人那里借），lend=借出（借给别人）。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': 'The teacher writes on the ___ with chalk. (board / desk / book)', 'options': ['board', 'desk', 'book', 'chair'], 'answer': 'board'}, {'question': 'Students ___ books from the library. (borrow / read / buy)', 'options': ['borrow', 'read', 'buy', 'write'], 'answer': 'borrow'}, {'question': '___ is the study of past events. (History / Geography / Science)', 'options': ['History', 'Geography', 'Science', 'Art'], 'answer': 'History'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '学校词汇关键区分：borrow vs lend, learn vs study, teacher vs professor。'}]}}, {'title': '交通与地点词汇', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 3, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '问路、描述地点是KET常见话题。掌握交通方式和地点词汇非常重要。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '交通与地点词汇', 'content': '交通方式：bus, train, car, bike, taxi, plane, underground/metro\n地点：hospital, bank, supermarket, restaurant, cinema, museum, park\n方位：next to, opposite, between, behind, in front of, near, far\n动作：turn left, turn right, go straight, cross the road'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'KET听力常考对话：问路', 'solution': "A: Excuse me, how do I get to the hospital?\nB: Go straight along this road, turn left at the traffic lights, and it's next to the park.\nA: Thank you very much!\nB: You're welcome."}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'Fill in: The cinema is ___ the bank and the restaurant. (between / next to / opposite)', 'solution': 'Answer: between. 在两者之间用between...and...。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': 'You can see old things in a ___. (museum / cinema / hospital)', 'options': ['museum', 'cinema', 'hospital', 'supermarket'], 'answer': 'museum'}, {'question': 'The school is ___ the park. You can walk there. (near / between / behind)', 'options': ['near', 'between', 'behind', 'opposite'], 'answer': 'near'}, {'question': '___ the road and turn right. (Cross / Go / Turn)', 'options': ['Cross', 'Go', 'Turn', 'Walk'], 'answer': 'Cross'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': "地点词汇配合方位介词使用：next to, opposite, between, near。问路三部曲：go straight, turn, it's on your left/right。"}]}}, {'title': '动词与形容词积累', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 4, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '动词和形容词是英语表达的灵魂。掌握常用动词和形容词能大幅提升阅读和写作能力。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '高频动词与形容词', 'content': '常用动词：enjoy, prefer, decide, agree, believe, suggest, invite, offer, provide, improve\n描述感觉：happy, sad, angry, excited, worried, tired, bored, surprised, interested, nervous\n描述事物：beautiful, comfortable, cheap, expensive, easy, difficult, important, interesting, popular, dangerous\n比较级：big→bigger→biggest, good→better→best, bad→worse→worst'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '用形容词比较级造句', 'solution': "例句：This book is more interesting than that one.\nMy room is bigger than my brother's room.\nEnglish is easier than math for me."}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'Fill in: I am ___ in science. I want to be a scientist. (interested / interesting)', 'solution': 'Answer: interested. 描述人的感受用-ed结尾(interested)，描述事物用-ing结尾(interesting)。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': 'She ___ to go to the park after school. (decided / enjoyed / believed)', 'options': ['decided', 'enjoyed', 'believed', 'suggested'], 'answer': 'decided'}, {'question': "The movie was ___. I didn't like it. (boring / bored)", 'options': ['boring', 'bored'], 'answer': 'boring'}, {'question': 'This is the ___ (good) restaurant in town. (best / better / good)', 'options': ['best', 'better', 'good', 'well'], 'answer': 'best'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '形容词重点：-ed描述感受，-ing描述事物。比较级加-er/-r，最高级加-est/-st。不规则：good→better→best。'}]}}]}, {'name': '阅读理解技巧', 'description': '掌握KET阅读理解的题型和解题策略', 'sort_order': 2, 'lessons': [{'title': '阅读理解概述', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 1, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': 'KET阅读理解有三部分。掌握正确策略很重要！'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': 'KET阅读题型', 'content': 'Part 1: 通知/标识理解 — 看懂公共场所的简短文字\nPart 2: 多文本匹配 — 将人物描述与文本匹配\nPart 3: 长文阅读 — 阅读理解选择题\nPart 4: 完形填空 — 选词填空\nPart 5: 开放式完形填空 — 不给选项，自己填词'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'Part 1例题：NO FOOD OR DRINKS IN THE LIBRARY. What does this mean?', 'solution': 'Answer: You cannot eat or drink in the library.\n解题技巧：NO... = You cannot/must not...'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'Part 3例题：Sarah likes swimming and playing tennis. She wants to find a sports center near her home.', 'solution': '在多个文本中找提到sports center且有swimming和tennis的选项。\n解题技巧：先读题目要求，再扫读文本找关键词。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': 'NOTICE: Please return books within 14 days. This means you must ___', 'options': ['return books in 2 weeks', 'buy the books', 'keep the books forever', 'return books tomorrow'], 'answer': 'return books in 2 weeks'}, {'question': 'The sign says "STAFF ONLY". Who can enter?', 'options': ['Only workers', 'Anyone', 'Only students', 'Only managers'], 'answer': 'Only workers'}, {'question': 'A text says "The museum is open from 9am to 5pm every day except Monday." When is it closed?', 'options': ['Monday', 'Weekends', 'Friday', 'Every day'], 'answer': 'Monday'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '阅读理解策略：先读题→找关键词→定位原文→理解上下文→选答案。'}]}}, {'title': '细节理解题', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 2, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '细节理解题是KET阅读最基础的题型。答案就在原文中，关键是准确定位。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '细节题解题技巧', 'content': '① 读题干，找出关键词（人名、地名、数字、特殊名词）\n② 在原文中扫描找到对应位置\n③ 比较选项和原文的表述\n④ 注意同义替换（原文说happy，选项可能说pleased）\n⑤ 排除法：去掉明显错误的选项'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '原文：The train to London leaves at 9:30 on weekdays and 10:00 on weekends.\n问题：When does the train leave on Saturday?', 'solution': 'Answer: 10:00. Saturday是weekend（周末），所以是10:00。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '原文：Emma bought a blue dress for $30 and a pair of shoes for $45.\n问题：How much did Emma spend in total?', 'solution': 'Answer: $75. 30 + 45 = 75. 注意题目问的是total（总共）。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '原文：The park opens at 8am and closes at 6pm in summer. How many hours is the park open in summer?', 'options': ['10 hours', '8 hours', '12 hours', '6 hours'], 'answer': '10 hours'}, {'question': '原文：Tom has three sisters and one brother. How many siblings does Tom have?', 'options': ['4', '3', '1', '5'], 'answer': '4'}, {'question': '原文：The sale ends on December 24th. Today is December 20th. How many days until the sale ends?', 'options': ['4', '5', '3', '6'], 'answer': '4'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '细节题：找关键词→定位原文→理解意思→选答案。注意同义替换和数字计算。'}]}}, {'title': '主旨大意题', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 3, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '主旨大意题考查对整篇文章的理解。不能只看某一句，要把握全文的中心思想。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '主旨题解题技巧', 'content': '① 读首尾段/首尾句，通常包含主旨\n② 问自己：这篇文章主要在说什么？\n③ 排除太具体或太宽泛的选项\n④ 正确答案应该涵盖全文内容\n⑤ 注意文章的标题和小标题'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '文章主要讲述了一个女孩学习弹钢琴的过程，从开始觉得困难到后来在比赛中获奖。\n问题：What is the main idea of the text?', 'solution': 'Answer: A girl learned to play the piano and succeeded.\n太具体的：She won a competition.（这只是其中一部分）\n太宽泛的：Music is important.（没有涉及具体人物）'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '一篇文章介绍了三种不同的环保方式：骑自行车、回收垃圾和节约用水。\n问题：What is the text mainly about?', 'solution': 'Answer: Different ways to protect the environment.\n而不是具体说某一种方式。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '文章讲述一个小镇每年举办音乐节，吸引了很多游客，促进了当地经济。主旨是？', 'options': ['A music festival helps a town', 'Music is fun', 'People like festivals', 'The town is big'], 'answer': 'A music festival helps a town'}, {'question': '文章介绍如何制作巧克力蛋糕，包括材料、步骤和小贴士。主旨是？', 'options': ['How to make a chocolate cake', 'Chocolate is delicious', 'Baking is a hobby', 'Cakes are popular'], 'answer': 'How to make a chocolate cake'}, {'question': '文章描述了北极熊面临的环境威胁和保护措施。主旨是？', 'options': ['Protecting polar bears', 'The Arctic is cold', 'Bears are strong', 'Climate change'], 'answer': 'Protecting polar bears'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '主旨题策略：读首尾段→概括全文→排除太具体/太宽泛选项→选最全面的答案。'}]}}, {'title': '推理判断题', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 4, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '推理判断题需要你根据文章信息进行合理推断，答案不是直接写在文中的。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '推理题解题技巧', 'content': '① 找到文中的线索/证据\n② 根据线索进行合理推断\n③ 不要选过度推断的答案\n④ 不要加入个人偏见\n⑤ 常见推理类型：人物感受、事件原因、未来发展'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '原文：Mark looked at his watch and started running. "I can\'t be late again!" he thought.\n问题：How does Mark probably feel?', 'solution': 'Answer: Worried/Anxious. 他看表后开始跑，说明他担心迟到。"can\'t be late again"表明之前已经迟到过。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '原文：The restaurant was empty. The waiter sat at a table reading a newspaper.\n问题：What can we infer about the restaurant?', 'solution': "Answer: It's not busy. 餐厅空的，服务员在看报纸，说明生意不好或不是营业高峰期。"}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': "原文：Jane put on her coat and umbrella before going out. What's the weather probably like?", 'options': ['Rainy', 'Sunny', 'Snowy', 'Hot'], 'answer': 'Rainy'}, {'question': '原文：Tom smiled when he saw his test result. He called his mom immediately. How did Tom do on the test?', 'options': ['Well', 'Poorly', 'Average', "He didn't finish"], 'answer': 'Well'}, {'question': '原文：The shop had a "50% OFF" sign in the window. There were many people inside. Why are there many people?', 'options': ['The prices are low', 'The shop is new', 'People are bored', "It's a holiday"], 'answer': 'The prices are low'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '推理题：找线索→合理推断→不主观臆断→选最有证据支持的答案。'}]}}]}, {'name': '完形填空', 'description': '掌握KET完形填空的解题方法和常见考点', 'sort_order': 3, 'lessons': [{'title': '完形填空解题策略', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 1, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '完形填空考查词汇、语法和上下文理解。掌握系统方法可以大幅提高正确率。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '完形填空三步法', 'content': '第一步：通读全文，了解大意（不急着选答案）\n第二步：逐空分析，利用上下文线索选答案\n第三步：通读检查，确保语法和逻辑正确\n常见考点：词汇辨析、固定搭配、语法结构、上下文逻辑'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'Tom is very ___ at math. He always gets 100 on his tests. (good / bad / slow / afraid)', 'solution': 'Answer: good. 后句说他总是考100分，说明他数学很好。good at是固定搭配。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'I ___ to school by bus every day. (go / went / am going / goes)', 'solution': 'Answer: go. every day表示习惯性动作，用一般现在时。主语I，所以用go。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': 'She ___ her homework before dinner yesterday. (finished / finishes / finishing / finish)', 'options': ['finished', 'finishes', 'finishing', 'finish'], 'answer': 'finished'}, {'question': 'The movie was so ___ that everyone laughed. (funny / sad / scary / boring)', 'options': ['funny', 'sad', 'scary', 'boring'], 'answer': 'funny'}, {'question': 'I have ___ friends in my new school. (many / much / little / less)', 'options': ['many', 'much', 'little', 'less'], 'answer': 'many'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '完形填空口诀：先通读、再逐空、后检查。注意时态、搭配和上下文逻辑。'}]}}, {'title': '词汇辨析', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 2, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '完形填空中很多题考查词汇辨析。区分形近词和义近词是必备技能。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '常考易混淆词', 'content': 'look/see/watch: look看(动作), see看到(结果), watch观看(持续)\nlisten/hear: listen听(动作), hear听到(结果)\nsay/tell/speak/talk: say说(内容), tell告诉(人), speak说(语言), talk交谈\nbring/take/carry: bring带来, take带走, carry搬运\nlearn/study: learn学到, study学习(过程)\nalso/too/either: also/too也(肯定), either也(否定)'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'Please ___ me the time. (tell / say / speak / talk)', 'solution': 'Answer: tell. tell somebody something是固定搭配。"告诉我时间"用tell。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'I can ___ a bird in the tree. (see / look / watch)', 'solution': 'Answer: see. 表示"看到"这个结果，用see。look是不及物动词，watch是持续观看。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': 'She can ___ three languages. (speak / say / tell / talk)', 'options': ['speak', 'say', 'tell', 'talk'], 'answer': 'speak'}, {'question': 'Please ___ this letter to your teacher. (take / bring / carry / get)', 'options': ['take', 'bring', 'carry', 'get'], 'answer': 'take'}, {'question': 'I like apples. My sister ___ likes them. (also / too / either)', 'options': ['also', 'too', 'either', 'neither'], 'answer': 'also'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '词汇辨析：注意动作vs结果(look/see)、方向(bring/take)、搭配(tell sb sth)。'}]}}, {'title': '固定搭配与语法', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 3, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '固定搭配和语法是完形填空的必考内容。掌握常见的搭配和语法规则。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '常考固定搭配', 'content': "be good at 擅长\nbe interested in 对...感兴趣\nlook forward to 期待\ndepend on 依靠\nbe proud of 为...自豪\nmake up one's mind 下定决心\non the other hand 另一方面\nin fact 事实上\nat least 至少\nby the way 顺便说一下"}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'She is very good ___ playing tennis. (at / in / on / for)', 'solution': 'Answer: at. be good at是固定搭配，意思是"擅长"。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "I'm looking forward ___ hearing from you. (to / at / for / in)", 'solution': 'Answer: to. look forward to中to是介词，后面跟-ing形式。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': 'He is interested ___ science. (in / at / on / for)', 'options': ['in', 'at', 'on', 'for'], 'answer': 'in'}, {'question': 'We are proud ___ our school. (of / at / in / for)', 'options': ['of', 'at', 'in', 'for'], 'answer': 'of'}, {'question': '___ the way, where is the nearest bank? (By / On / In / At)', 'options': ['By', 'On', 'In', 'At'], 'answer': 'By'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '固定搭配没有捷径，只能多记多练。遇到不熟悉的搭配记在笔记本上。'}]}}, {'title': '完形填空综合练习', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 4, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '综合运用前面学到的技巧来做完形填空练习。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '综合练习要点', 'content': '① 先读全文了解大意\n② 利用上下文线索\n③ 检查语法是否正确\n④ 验证逻辑是否通顺\n⑤ 实在不确定就用排除法'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "Dear Tom, I'm writing to ___ you about my new school. It's very big ___ beautiful. There ___ about 500 students. The teachers are very friendly. I have ___ new friends here. I ___ my old school, but I like this one too.\nPlease write back soon!\nBest wishes, Lisa", 'solution': '① tell (tell sb about sth)\n② and (连接big和beautiful)\n③ are (500 students是复数)\n④ many/some (friends可数)\n⑤ miss (想念旧学校)'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'Last weekend, my family ___ to the beach. The weather ___ sunny and warm. We ___ in the sea and ___ sandcastles. In the evening, we ___ seafood at a restaurant. It ___ a wonderful day!', 'solution': '① went (go to the beach, 过去时)\n② was (天气was)\n③ swam (swim的过去式)\n④ built (build sandcastles, 过去式)\n⑤ ate (eat的过去式)\n⑥ was (总结性描述)'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': "I ___ my key this morning and couldn't get into the house. (lost / found / saw / bought)", 'options': ['lost', 'found', 'saw', 'bought'], 'answer': 'lost'}, {'question': 'The children were ___ because it was their birthday. (excited / bored / tired / angry)', 'options': ['excited', 'bored', 'tired', 'angry'], 'answer': 'excited'}, {'question': "If it ___ tomorrow, we'll stay at home. (rains / rained / will rain / raining)", 'options': ['rains', 'rained', 'will rain', 'raining'], 'answer': 'rains'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '完形填空综合：先读→逐空分析→检查。注意时态一致、搭配正确、逻辑通顺。'}]}}]}, {'name': '信息匹配', 'description': '掌握KET信息匹配题型的解题技巧', 'sort_order': 4, 'lessons': [{'title': '信息匹配题型分析', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 1, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '信息匹配题要求你将人物描述与相应的文本进行匹配。关键是要抓住每个人的特殊需求。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '信息匹配策略', 'content': '① 先读每个人的描述，标注关键词\n② 扫读所有文本，不要细读\n③ 每个描述找2-3个匹配特征\n④ 注意排除干扰项\n⑤ 一个人可能匹配多个文本，选最合适的'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'Tom wants to play football with friends on Saturday morning. He needs to find a place nearby.', 'solution': '关键词：football, Saturday morning, nearby\n扫读文本找：sports, football, weekend, morning, near/close\n匹配：找提到足球场且周末开放的'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': 'Lisa is looking for a gift for her mother. Her mother likes reading. Lisa has $20.', 'solution': '关键词：gift, mother, reading/books, $20\n匹配：找书店、价格$20以内的推荐'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': 'Bob wants to learn to cook Italian food. He is free on Wednesday evenings. What should he look for?', 'options': ['Italian cooking class on Wednesday evening', 'French cooking class on Saturday', 'Italian restaurant', 'Wednesday evening class'], 'answer': 'Italian cooking class on Wednesday evening'}, {'question': "Emma needs a hotel near the airport for one night. She doesn't want to spend more than $80.", 'options': ['Airport hotel under $80', 'City center hotel $120', 'Airport hotel $100', 'Beach hotel $60'], 'answer': 'Airport hotel under $80'}, {'question': 'Jack wants to buy a cheap laptop for school. Which should he choose?', 'options': ['Student laptop deal $300', 'Gaming laptop $1500', 'Phone $500', 'Desktop computer $800'], 'answer': 'Student laptop deal $300'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '信息匹配：先标注关键词→扫读找匹配→验证条件→选最佳。'}]}}, {'title': '快速扫读技巧', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 2, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '快速扫读(scanning)是信息匹配的核心技能。学会快速定位关键信息。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '扫读技巧', 'content': '① 不要逐字阅读，跳着找关键词\n② 注意标题、粗体字、数字、大写词\n③ 先读问题再看文本\n④ 用手指或笔引导视线\n⑤ 时间压力下先做最有把握的'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '扫读这段找价格：The Grand Hotel is located in the city center. It has 200 rooms, a swimming pool, and two restaurants. Room prices start from $150 per night. Breakfast is included.', 'solution': '价格信息：$150 per night. 其余信息（位置、设施）可以先跳过。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '扫读找时间：The museum opens at 9:00 AM from Tuesday to Sunday. It closes at 5:00 PM. On Mondays, the museum is closed. Special late opening until 8:00 PM on Fridays.', 'solution': '开放时间：Tue-Sun 9AM-5PM, 周一关门, 周五延长至8PM'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '扫读找电话号码：For more information, please contact us at 555-1234 or email info@example.com.', 'options': ['555-1234', 'info@example.com', 'more information', 'please contact'], 'answer': '555-1234'}, {'question': '扫读找日期：The concert will be held on March 15th, 2025 at the City Hall.', 'options': ['March 15th, 2025', 'concert', 'City Hall', 'held'], 'answer': 'March 15th, 2025'}, {'question': '扫读找限制：Children under 5 can enter for free. Adults: $10, Students: $7.', 'options': ['Children under 5 free', '$10', '$7', 'enter'], 'answer': 'Children under 5 free'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '扫读：带着问题找答案，不逐字阅读，关注数字、日期、名称等关键信息。'}]}}, {'title': '信息匹配实战', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 3, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '这节课我们通过完整的信息匹配练习来巩固技巧。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '实战要点', 'content': '① 先读所有人的需求（1分钟）\n② 标注每个人的2-3个关键需求\n③ 快速扫读所有文本\n④ 逐一匹配，不确定的先跳过\n⑤ 用排除法处理剩余的'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '人物A: Mike wants to buy a birthday present for his girlfriend. She likes music and jewelry. Budget: $50.\n人物B: Sarah wants to find a restaurant for her birthday dinner. She has 10 friends coming. She likes Italian food.\n文本1: Music Box Store - CDs, headphones, and music gifts from $10 to $100\n文本2: Bella Italia - Italian restaurant, groups welcome, booking required', 'solution': 'Mike → Music Box Store ($50内的音乐礼物)\nSarah → Bella Italia (意大利餐厅，可接待团队)'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '人物C: David is looking for a gym. He works until 6pm. He wants to swim.\n文本3: FitLife Gym - Open 6am-10pm daily. Swimming pool, basketball court. $30/month.\n文本4: Quick Fit - Open 7am-7pm. No pool. $20/month.', 'solution': 'David → FitLife Gym (营业到10pm，有游泳池)'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': "Amy wants a quiet place to study. She needs Wi-Fi. She doesn't like coffee shops. Which place? Library or Internet cafe?", 'options': ['Library', 'Internet cafe', 'Coffee shop', 'Home'], 'answer': 'Library'}, {'question': 'Tom needs new running shoes. Size 43. He wants to spend less than $60. Store A: Running shoes $50-80. Store B: Running shoes $30-55.', 'options': ['Store B', 'Store A', 'Both stores', 'Online'], 'answer': 'Store B'}, {'question': 'Lisa wants to watch a movie on Saturday night. She likes comedies. Cinema A: Action movies. Cinema B: Comedies and dramas.', 'options': ['Cinema B', 'Cinema A', 'Both', 'Neither'], 'answer': 'Cinema B'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '信息匹配实战：快速标注需求→高效扫读→精准匹配→验证条件。'}]}}, {'title': '匹配题综合训练', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 4, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '最后一节信息匹配课，我们做综合训练来提升速度和准确率。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '速度提升技巧', 'content': '① 训练自己1分钟内读完3-4个文本\n② 练习用关键词快速判断\n③ 不要纠结于生词\n④ 整体理解优先于细节\n⑤ 每天做1-2篇保持手感'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '综合训练：匹配5个人的需求到8个文本', 'solution': '步骤：\n1. 读5个需求，每个标注2个关键词（1分钟）\n2. 扫读8个文本，每个花10秒（1.5分钟）\n3. 先匹配最明显的（0.5分钟）\n4. 处理较难的匹配（1分钟）\n5. 检查（0.5分钟）\n总共约5分钟'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '错误分析：常见错误是把文本中的某个词和需求中的某个词相同就匹配，忽略了整体意思。', 'solution': '正确做法：匹配时要确保主要需求都满足。\n例如：需求是"安静的餐厅"，文本提到"restaurant"但说"very noisy"，不能匹配。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': 'Karen wants to learn Spanish. She is free on weekends only. Course A: Spanish, Mon/Wed. Course B: Spanish, Sat/Sun.', 'options': ['Course B', 'Course A', 'Neither', 'Both'], 'answer': 'Course B'}, {'question': 'Paul needs a pet-friendly apartment. 2 bedrooms. Under $1000. Apt 1: $900, 2br, no pets. Apt 2: $950, 2br, pets OK.', 'options': ['Apt 2', 'Apt 1', 'Both', 'Neither'], 'answer': 'Apt 2'}, {'question': 'Jenny is looking for a part-time job. She can work evenings. Job A: Weekend mornings. Job B: Monday-Friday evenings.', 'options': ['Job B', 'Job A', 'Both', 'Neither'], 'answer': 'Job B'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '信息匹配提速：关键词标注→快速扫读→先易后难→验证匹配。每天练习保持状态。'}]}}]}, {'name': '短消息写作', 'description': '掌握KET短消息写作的格式和技巧', 'sort_order': 5, 'lessons': [{'title': '短消息写作基础', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 1, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': 'KET写作Part 6要求写一条25-35词的短消息。掌握格式和常用句型是关键。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '短消息写作要点', 'content': '字数：25-35词（不能少于25或超过35）\n格式：根据题目要求（邮件、短信、便条）\n必须覆盖所有内容点（通常3个）\n使用简单但正确的英语\n注意拼写和标点'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '题目：你刚搬到新城市。写一封邮件给朋友，告诉他们：1. 你对新房子的感受 2. 描述你的邻居 3. 邀请他们来参观', 'solution': "Dear Emma,\nI love my new house! It's big and bright. My neighbors are very friendly and helpful. They have a cute dog. Please come and visit me soon!\nBest wishes,\nLisa (34 words)"}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '题目：你迟到了。写短信给老师说明：1. 原因 2. 大概几点到 3. 道歉', 'solution': "Dear Mr. Smith, I'm sorry but I'll be late for class today. My bus didn't come on time. I'll arrive at about 9:30. I apologize for the inconvenience. Tom (31 words)"}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '题目：邀请朋友参加你的生日派对。需要包含：日期、地点、希望他们来。以下哪句最好？', 'options': ['My birthday party is on Saturday at my house. I hope you can come!', 'Party Saturday. Come.', "I'm having a birthday party. It would be great if you could join us on Saturday at my house. Please come!"], 'answer': 'My birthday party is on Saturday at my house. I hope you can come!'}, {'question': '短消息字数要求是？', 'options': ['25-35词', '50-80词', '100词以上', '没有限制'], 'answer': '25-35词'}, {'question': '短消息必须做到？', 'options': ['覆盖所有内容点', '使用高级词汇', '写满100词', '只回答一个问题'], 'answer': '覆盖所有内容点'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '短消息写作：覆盖3个内容点+控制字数25-35词+拼写语法正确。'}]}}, {'title': '常用写作句型', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 2, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '掌握一些常用句型可以让你快速写出高质量的短消息。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '按功能分类的句型', 'content': "邀请：Would you like to...? / I'd like to invite you to...\n建议：Why don't you...? / You should... / How about...?\n道歉：I'm sorry for/about... / I apologize for...\n感谢：Thank you for... / Thanks for... / I really appreciate...\n请求：Could you please...? / Can you...? / I'd like to...\n描述：It's really... / I think it's... / The best thing is..."}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '写短信邀请朋友看电影', 'solution': "Hi Sam! Would you like to go to the cinema with me this weekend? There's a new comedy showing. It starts at 7pm. Let me know! (27 words)"}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '写邮件感谢朋友帮忙', 'solution': "Dear Jane, Thank you so much for helping me with my project yesterday. Your ideas were really helpful. I couldn't have done it without you! Best, Mary (30 words)"}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '邀请句型？', 'options': ['Would you like to...', "I don't want to...", 'You must...', 'Go away'], 'answer': 'Would you like to...'}, {'question': '道歉句型？', 'options': ["I'm sorry for...", "It's your fault", 'Whatever', 'No worries'], 'answer': "I'm sorry for..."}, {'question': '请求句型？', 'options': ['Could you please...', 'Do it now', 'I order you to', 'Never mind'], 'answer': 'Could you please...'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '记住6类功能句型：邀请、建议、道歉、感谢、请求、描述。考试时直接套用。'}]}}, {'title': '短消息写作实战', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 3, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '通过实战练习来巩固短消息写作技巧。这节课我们写不同类型的短消息。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '实战要点', 'content': '① 先列出3个内容点\n② 每个内容点写1-2句\n③ 控制总词数25-35\n④ 检查拼写和语法\n⑤ 添加合适的开头和结尾'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '题目：你的英国朋友要来你的城市旅游。写邮件告诉ta：1. 天气如何 2. 推荐一个景点 3. 建议穿什么', 'solution': "Dear Jack, I'm so excited you're visiting! The weather here is warm and sunny now. You should visit the old town – it's beautiful. Bring comfortable shoes for walking. Can't wait to see you! Best, Anna (36 words - 需要删减到35词内)\n修改：Dear Jack, Great you're visiting! It's warm and sunny here now. Visit the old town – it's beautiful. Bring comfortable shoes. See you soon! Anna (25 words)"}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '题目：你在图书馆发现了一个钱包。写短信给朋友说：1. 在哪发现的 2. 里面有什么 3. 你打算怎么办', 'solution': "Hi Mike! I found a wallet in the library today. It has some money and a student card inside. I'm going to take it to the office. Talk later! (32 words)"}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '题目：告诉老师你不能参加明天的考试。需要说明：原因、请求补考、道歉。以下哪段最好？', 'options': ["Dear teacher, I'm sick and can't take tomorrow's exam. I apologize. Can I take it later? Thank you.", "I don't want to take the exam.", 'The exam is tomorrow.'], 'answer': "Dear teacher, I'm sick and can't take tomorrow's exam. I apologize. Can I take it later? Thank you."}, {'question': '题目：你搬家了，通知朋友新地址。需包含：新地址、电话号码不变、欢迎来玩。', 'options': ['Hi! I moved to 123 Main Street. My phone number is the same. Please visit me!', 'I moved. Bye.', 'New address coming soon.'], 'answer': 'Hi! I moved to 123 Main Street. My phone number is the same. Please visit me!'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '短消息实战：列内容点→逐点写→控制字数→检查语法。记住开头和结尾格式。'}]}}, {'title': '写作常见错误与提升', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 4, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '避免常见错误可以让你的写作分数大幅提升。这节课我们来分析常见错误。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '五大常见错误', 'content': '① 主谓不一致：He like → He likes\n② 时态错误：Yesterday I go → Yesterday I went\n③ 拼写错误：beautful → beautiful\n④ 词序错误：I very like → I really like / I like...very much\n⑤ 标点错误：缺少句号或逗号'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '错误：Yesterday I go to park and I see my friend.', 'solution': '修正：Yesterday I went to the park and I saw my friend.\n错误分析：yesterday表过去→用过去时went, saw。park前需要the。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "错误：She don't likes apple. She very want a banana.", 'solution': "修正：She doesn't like apples. She really wants a banana.\n错误分析：第三人称用doesn't，like不加s。apples用复数。very不能修饰动词，用really。"}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '找出错误：He go to school every day.', 'options': ['go → goes', 'school → schools', 'day → days', 'He → They'], 'answer': 'go → goes'}, {'question': '找出错误：I am agree with you.', 'options': ['am agree → agree', 'with → to', 'you → your', 'I → Me'], 'answer': 'am agree → agree'}, {'question': '找出错误：She cans swim very good.', 'options': ['cans → can, good → well', 'swim → swims', 'very → much', 'She → He'], 'answer': 'cans → can, good → well'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '写作提升：主谓一致、时态正确、拼写准确、词序正确、标点完整。写完后检查一遍。'}]}}]}, {'name': '故事写作', 'description': '掌握KET故事写作的结构和技巧', 'sort_order': 6, 'lessons': [{'title': '故事写作结构', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 1, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': 'KET写作Part 7要求根据三张图片写一个35词以上的故事。掌握故事结构是第一步。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '故事三段式结构', 'content': '开头（Setting）：介绍人物、时间、地点\n中间（Problem/Action）：发生了什么事？遇到什么问题？\n结尾（Resolution）：问题如何解决？结局如何？\n\n连接词：First, Then, Next, After that, Finally, In the end'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '根据图片写故事：图1-男孩在公园踢球 图2-球飞到树上 图3-大人帮他拿下来', 'solution': "One Saturday, Tom was playing football in the park. Suddenly, he kicked the ball too hard and it went up into a tall tree. Tom tried to reach it but couldn't. Then, a kind man walked by and helped him get the ball down. Tom was very happy and thanked the man. (54 words)"}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '根据图片写故事：图1-女孩在书店看书 图2-她想买但钱不够 图3-朋友借钱给她', 'solution': "Last Sunday, Emma went to a bookshop and found a book she really wanted. But when she checked her pocket, she didn't have enough money. She felt sad. Just then, her friend Lisa came and lent her some money. Emma bought the book and promised to return the money soon. (52 words)"}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '故事三段式结构是？', 'options': ['开头-中间-结尾', '问题-答案-总结', '论点-论据-结论', '起因-经过-结果'], 'answer': '开头-中间-结尾'}, {'question': '故事连接词"然后"用英语说是？', 'options': ['Then / Next', 'But', 'Because', 'So'], 'answer': 'Then / Next'}, {'question': '故事结尾通常包含？', 'options': ['问题如何解决', '新的问题', '更多人物', '重复开头'], 'answer': '问题如何解决'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '故事写作：开头介绍→中间冲突→结尾解决。用连接词串联。写35词以上。'}]}}, {'title': '故事写作词汇与句型', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 2, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '掌握故事写作的常用词汇和句型，让你的故事更生动流畅。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '故事写作词汇', 'content': '时间词：one day, last weekend, yesterday, in the morning\n动作词：went, saw, heard, found, decided, ran, called, helped\n感受词：happy, excited, surprised, worried, scared, sad, angry\n转折词：but, however, suddenly, unfortunately\n结果词：so, therefore, finally, in the end'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '用丰富的词汇改写：She went to school. She saw a cat. She was happy.', 'solution': '改进：Yesterday morning, Emma walked to school happily. On the way, she noticed a cute orange cat sitting under a tree. She smiled and said hello to it.'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '用连接词串联：Tom was hungry. He went to the kitchen. He made a sandwich.', 'solution': '改进：Tom was really hungry, so he went to the kitchen. First, he took out some bread. Then, he added cheese and tomato. Finally, his delicious sandwich was ready!'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '故事开头常用哪个时间词？', 'options': ['One day / Last weekend', 'Usually', 'Always', 'Tomorrow'], 'answer': 'One day / Last weekend'}, {'question': '表示突然的转折词是？', 'options': ['Suddenly', 'Because', 'Also', 'And'], 'answer': 'Suddenly'}, {'question': '表示结果的连接词是？', 'options': ['So / Therefore', 'But / However', 'And / Also', 'If / Unless'], 'answer': 'So / Therefore'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '故事词汇：时间词开头+动作词推进+感受词表达+转折词制造悬念+结果词收尾。'}]}}, {'title': '故事写作实战', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 3, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '通过完整的故事写作练习来巩固所有技巧。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '实战步骤', 'content': '① 仔细看三张图片（30秒）\n② 确定故事主线：谁、在哪里、发生了什么\n③ 列出关键词（1分钟）\n④ 写故事，注意连接词和时态\n⑤ 检查字数和语法（1分钟）'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '图片：1.一家人在打包行李 2.他们开车去海边 3.他们在海滩上玩耍', 'solution': 'Last summer, the Smith family decided to go on holiday. First, they packed their bags with clothes and sunscreen. Then, they drove to the beach. The weather was perfect! The children built sandcastles and swam in the sea. They had a wonderful time together. (48 words)'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '图片：1.女孩看到一只迷路的小狗 2.她带小狗回家并喂食 3.她帮小狗找到了主人', 'solution': 'One rainy afternoon, Lucy found a small dog wandering on the street. It looked cold and hungry. She took it home and gave it some food and water. Then, she made some posters. The next day, the owner called. He was so happy and grateful! (48 words)'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '写故事时应该用什么时态？', 'options': ['过去时', '现在时', '将来时', '现在完成时'], 'answer': '过去时'}, {'question': '故事写作Part 7最低字数要求是？', 'options': ['35词', '25词', '50词', '100词'], 'answer': '35词'}, {'question': '写故事前应该先做什么？', 'options': ['仔细看图片确定主线', '直接开始写', '查字典', '问老师'], 'answer': '仔细看图片确定主线'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '故事写作实战：看图→定主线→列关键词→写作→检查。注意时态一致和字数达标。'}]}}, {'title': '故事写作提升技巧', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 4, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '学习一些高级技巧让你的故事写作更加出色，争取更高分数。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '提升技巧', 'content': '① 使用直接引语让故事更生动：She said, "Don\'t worry!"\n② 加入形容词和副词：big, beautiful, quickly, carefully\n③ 变化句式：不要所有句子都用相同结构\n④ 使用过去进行时设定场景：She was walking when...\n⑤ 用感官描写：It tasted sweet. It sounded beautiful.'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '普通版：Tom went to the park. He played football. He was happy.', 'solution': '提升版：On a sunny Saturday, Tom ran excitedly to the park. He and his friends played an exciting football match. "Goal!" he shouted happily. In the end, his team won, and he felt amazing.'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '加入感官描写：The cake was good. → The cake smelled wonderful and tasted deliciously sweet.', 'solution': '改进：The chocolate cake smelled amazing as it came out of the oven. When she took the first bite, it tasted wonderfully sweet and creamy.'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '直接引语的作用是？', 'options': ['让故事更生动', '增加字数', '展示语法', '替代描写'], 'answer': '让故事更生动'}, {'question': '过去进行时的作用是？', 'options': ['设定故事背景/场景', '表示将来', '表示习惯', '表示否定'], 'answer': '设定故事背景/场景'}, {'question': '变化句式意味着？', 'options': ['使用不同的句子结构', '每句都不同', '只用长句', '只用短句'], 'answer': '使用不同的句子结构'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '故事提升：直接引语+形容词副词+变化句式+过去进行时+感官描写。恭喜完成KET阅读与写作课程！'}]}}]}]
